data.description: GORGEOUS Villa in popular Rosewood Village - ONLY 2 YEARS OLD! 3 HUGE Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms, bright & open floor plan, Kitchen with large island, quartz counters, and gas stove, dining area, Living Room open to second story.  Main level Primary suite features a large walk-in closet and a full Bathroom with soaking tub, separate shower, and double vanity.  Half Bathroom and Laundry finish out the main level.  Upstairs you'll find 2 more Bedrooms and a large Loft perfect for a Family Room, office, etc.  Plenty of parking with the 2-car garage and large driveway.  Very Convenient location close to the college, hospital, shopping, restaurants, and interstate.
